939
01:14:28,779 --> 01:14:30,079
dedaunan tumbuh,

940
01:14:30,619 --> 01:14:32,319
bunga-bunga bermekaran, lalu gugur.

941
01:14:35,319 --> 01:14:38,489
Apa Nona ingin melihatnya

